{"tid":1692831,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"草娥消失2年首曝光","createTime":"2019-11-04T09:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T13:03:19.000Z","uid":74065,"like":23,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac1edb0adc19cd88df0a576de9b306aaf7ee2fe","tid":1692831,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:18:32.000Z","msg":"南韓女團AOA最近剛以5人體制參加綜藝節目《Queendom》，證明寶刀未老的實力，粉絲不禁好奇退團的成員近況。最近就有粉絲捕獲野生前主唱草娥，並成功要求自合照，消失2年的她首度露面，看起來氣色很好，而也有網友挖出鼓手有慶正在當YouTuber，拍攝內容讓粉絲都鼻酸！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4484/d4484908.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4484%2Fd4484908.jpg&h=dbac35e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n草娥消失2年首曝光...及胸長髮美炸！（圖／翻攝自韓網、AOA臉書）<br />\n<br />\n據韓網最新流出的照片中，一名男子與草娥自拍，表示是去參加一場婚宴而遇到草娥，因此要求合照。照片中草娥留著及胸的長髮，空氣瀏海更顯清純，畫上深色眼線以及穿著有領外套的端莊服飾，讓粉絲看到十分感動，「等了2年終於看到妳」、「姐姐真的好美」。<br />\n<br />\n其實AOA剛創團時曾組子分隊「AOA Black」，以女子樂團方式演出，但因為舞蹈表演方式較吃香，樂團漸漸式微，而其中一位擔任鼓手的有慶則漸漸淡出，2016年底就已退團。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4484/d4484909.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4484%2Fd4484909.jpg&h=1706357c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粉絲也關心她的近況，原來有慶1年前開始拍攝YouTube影片，並上傳在YouTube「You's Drum」帳號轉當YouTuber，而她拍攝的內容，大部分都是練習打鼓，包含TWICE、BTS等歌曲，可以發現她坐在鼓前隨著音樂搖晃身體、非常享受。粉絲看哭，「原來有慶還繼續堅持著夢想」、「姐姐加油」。而她染著金髮的模樣也被大讚美貌升級了！"},{"pid":"efd2591f2cdf0e25b5f77dc0004dfb1444aea121","tid":1692831,"uid":189235,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:20:51.000Z","msg":"無咗陣淫味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12330d4681966a6d36f2686d865bfba4f84a7188","tid":1692831,"uid":76632,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:23:06.000Z","msg":"heart attack她<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"c32d0fde5c3396148108e95cafc287ec4a1ded10","tid":1692831,"uid":3405,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:36:25.000Z","msg":"choa先係最正嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8807eecec249181062dda84bdccb7168dfd402d4","tid":1692831,"uid":76098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:39:29.000Z","msg":"係開心既"},{"pid":"2bcd46bbf23565d7bcfb19fb28365a3c93132394","tid":1692831,"uid":211295,"like":9,"dislike":20,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:40:59.000Z","msg":"月娥我就識"},{"pid":"b11e93716c74dee719f279720756433f9cc5789b","tid":1692831,"uid":58140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:41:54.000Z","msg":"choa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8a2d6fbc9818ed897cf17a529a57f7fda25931","tid":1692831,"uid":152123,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:42:27.000Z","msg":"死啦認唔出&hellip;"},{"pid":"48cb3e4b827b86a79d1f392807ba67f5b890903e","tid":1692831,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:45:14.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"75014fa929ad745869f27c8c641f2e379d75e5d3","tid":1692831,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa8a2d6fbc9818ed897cf17a529a57f7fda25931","tid":1692831,"uid":152123,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:42:27.000Z","msg":"死啦認唔出&hellip;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:46:50.000Z","msg":"==都冇乜變"},{"pid":"0d1e326fcb8325865d7ed5730fd7bc8639fc2953","tid":1692831,"uid":229026,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:05:52.000Z","msg":"個樣純咗咁多"},{"pid":"ad78825a13c2820e11581f557d4ee1b3aace70c9","tid":1692831,"uid":309529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11